      {
        "question": "How often do I need twin interval scans?",
        "answer": "Monochorionic every 2 weeks; dichorionic every 3–4 weeks."
      },
      {
        "question": "Is the scan painful?",
        "answer": "No—just mild pressure."
      },
      {
        "question": "Can I eat before the scan?",
